<p>Especially for the <strong>Indian climate and lifestyle</strong>, maintaining healthy hair and skin requires specialized care that addresses local environmental factors, diet, and genetics.</p>

<h2>White Hair Kyun Hote Hain? — Melanin Ka Science</h2>
        <p>Sabfrom pehle yeh samajhna zaroori hai of white hair actually hote kyun hain. Humare har ek hair follicle mein <strong>melanocytes</strong> happen — yeh special cells hain jo <strong>melanin</strong> pigment produce karte hain. Melanin hi humari hair ko black, brown ya dark color deta hai.</p>
        <p>Jab yeh melanocytes kaam karna band kar dete hain ya melanin production reduce ho jaata hai, toh naye hair bina color ke ugte hain — yaani white ya grey dikhte hain. Yeh process naturally ageing ke saath hota hai, lekin bahut from logon mein yeh bahut jaldi shuru ho jaata hai — isko hum <strong>premature greying</strong> kehte hain.</p>
        <p>Premature greying ke main reasons hain:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Genetics:</strong> Agar aapke parents ko early white hair aaye the, toh aapko also aane ke chances zyada hain</li>
          <li><strong>Vitamin deficiency:</strong> Khaas tand par <a href="which-vitamin-deficiency-causes-white-hair.php">Vitamin B12, D, Iron and Zinc of kami</a> from white hair jaldi aate hain</li>
          <li><strong>Oxidative stress:</strong> Free radicals melanocytes ko damage karte hain</li>
          <li><strong>Chronic stress:</strong> Mental stress melanocyte stem cells ko khatam karta hai</li>
          <li><strong>Smoking and poor lifestyle:</strong> Yeh premature ageing ko accelerate karte hain</li>
          <li><strong>Thyroid and hormonal imbalance:</strong> Hormonal changes also melanin production ko affect karte hain</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Zyada detail mein jaanna hai toh humare blog <a href="why-hair-become-white.php">why hair become white</a> ko zaroor padhein — wahan humne melanin loss ka poora science explain ofya hai.</p>

        
